<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-sRIl4kxILFvY47J16cr9ZwB07vP4J8+LH7qKQnuqkuIAvNWLzeN8tE5YBujZqJLB" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/validation.css">
    <title>complete</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="about-store" id="about-store">
        <h1>لقد تم استلام طلبك بنجاح!</h1>

        <p>رقم الطلب: <%= order._id %></p>
        <p>الكمية: <%= order.quantity %></p>
        <p>الوقت: <%= order.time %></p>

        <p>سيتم الاتصال بك عندما يجهز طلبك 📞</p>
        <div class="alert alert-danger d-flex align-items-center" role="alert">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill flex-shrink-0 me-2" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Warning:">
                <path d="M8.982 1.566a1.13 1.13 0 0 0-1.96 0L.165 13.233c-.457.778.091 1.767.98 1.767h13.713c.889 0 1.438-.99.98-1.767L8.982 1.566zM8 5c.535 0 .954.462.9.995l-.35 3.507a.552.552 0 0 1-1.1 0L7.1 5.995A.905.905 0 0 1 8 5zm.002 6a1 1 0 1 1 0 2 1 1 0 0 1 0-2z"/>
            </svg>
        <div>تنبيه! الاتصال يجري من خلال ذكاء اصطناعي</div>
</div>
    <br>
    <hr>
    <br>
        <a href="/" class="submit-btn">الرجوع للرئيسية</a>
    </div>

    <style>
        a{
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
            <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-FKyoEForCGlyvwx9Hj09JcYn3nv7wiPVlz7YYwJrWVcXK/BmnVDxM+D2scQbITxI" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>